00:00:40.062 --> 00:00:44.025
So the Birthday Problem
is very simple to state.

00:00:44.025 --> 00:00:48.997
The problem is just, you have a group
of people at a party, or something.

00:00:48.997 --> 00:00:53.753
And you wanna know how likely is it
that two people have the same birthday.

00:00:53.753 --> 00:00:56.049
Maybe three people will
have the same birthday,

00:00:56.049 --> 00:00:58.850
